Peabody & Co. in New York, joins the firm as institutional equity manager, and 
David Hirschhorn of Nikko Securities in New York will become vice president for 
corporate finance. 
</P>
<P>
 "Their expertise in the institutional and retail brokerage arenas will help 
maintain our current aggressive rate of growth and help us to continue to 
provide quality service to our clients," Chairman Walter C. Cruttenden III 
said. 
