 Reader Carol Close recalls when she and her husband took their children to see 
"Aladdin": 
</P>
<P>
 "Just when Aladdin kisses Jasmine, and through the din of all the kids in the 
theater booing, I thought I heard my 5-year-old son Collin exclaim: 'They're 
