BRIEFLY: COMPANY TOWN ANNEX 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Staff and Wire Reports 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Spielberg in Deal With Knowledge Adventure: Director and producer Steven 
Spielberg signed an agreement to develop educational software with multimedia 
publisher Knowledge Adventure.He will also make an equity investment in the La 
Crescenta-based firm. Plans call for Spielberg to develop original titles using 
Knowledge Adventure's technology. He may also help add stories and characters 
to the 2-year-old firm's CD-ROM educational titles for children, such as "Body 
Adventure" and "Dinosaur Adventure." 
</P>
