</P>
<P>
 Barefoot Cellars wines will accompany a meal at JW's restaurant Friday night. 
</P>
<P>
 The dinner ($29 a person, plus tax and tip) begins with tropical fruit salad 
and white Zinfandel. Following are scallop pot stickers with Sauvignon blanc, a 
white corn souffle with a Chardonnay and a beef dish served with a Cabernet. 
</P>
<P>
 Seating is by reservation only, between 6 and 10 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
 Anaheim Marriott, 700 W. Convention Way. (714) 750-0900. 
