 California Pizza Kitchen opened its 55th restaurant on Monday, in Mission 
Viejo. As at its other locations, the Pizza Kitchen is offering 29 varieties of 
pizzas, including its signature Thai chicken, shrimp-pesto and Caribbean shrimp 
pizzas. 
</P>
<P>
 Hours are Sunday through Thursday, 11:30 a.m. to 10 p.m.; Friday and Saturday 
till 11 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
 25513 Marguerite Parkway. (714) 951-5026. 
</P>
<P>
 * 
</P>
<P>
 Piret's Gallery Bistro will host an artist's reception tonight from 6 to 9 to 
showcase the paintings of Ann Marie Anderson, which are on display at the 
bistro through October. 
</P>
<P>
 Anderson's works reflect her classical-art background and her training in 
Thailand and Japan. The reception, which is free and open to the public, 
includes appetizers and wine. 
</P>
<P>
 3333 Bristol St., at the Carousel entrance to South Coast Plaza, Costa Mesa. 
(714) 556-6424. 
</P>
<P>
