 Voter Turnout Percentage of registered voters who voted. Party: Registered 
Voters (% Voted) Republican: 602,291 (35.6) Democratic: 397,105 (30.9) 
Libertarian: 6,968 (20.3) Green: 3,101 (18.9) American Independent: 19,593 
(12.0) Peace & Freedom: 3,626 (8.3) others, declined to state: 121,010 (16.8) 
Totals: 1,153,694 (31.4) Note: Does not include uncounted absentee ballots 
</P>
